{"tid":598383,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"【I/A】Brown Dust (9) - 面對黎緊既新角,歌雞同綠盾都只係垃圾黎","createTime":"2018-03-19T12:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T12:56:56.000Z","uid":1522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"38e05aecc9bb24c1db875f0ef88aaf19abbd8fb7","tid":598383,"uid":1522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:38:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">韓國 NEOWIZ 3月6日宣佈戰略指令RPG《Brown Dust》（iOS/Android）預定於3月7日正式配信。</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195505_47e0b0012668b40f6186d1601bdaf883.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195505_47e0b0012668b40f6186d1601bdaf883.jpg&h=ea74ebf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195509_8788c08b0778aae6ff1a0aad46096130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195509_8788c08b0778aae6ff1a0aad46096130.jpg&h=4187a89f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195512_e66449a702abdae8637047bf9e29d66b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195512_e66449a702abdae8637047bf9e29d66b.jpg&h=2de03b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195516_7da5ea65940162c195614437c60069d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195516_7da5ea65940162c195614437c60069d3.jpg&h=ebf17d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195525_c9708864050718f395240c097b62ccbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195525_c9708864050718f395240c097b62ccbd.jpg&h=aa273b19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195417_7a56d2bff3b5268a5d22dc56ff713f79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195417_7a56d2bff3b5268a5d22dc56ff713f79.jpg&h=e3b49087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195425_74d2e66348966c75afb1de4dc71a9798.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195425_74d2e66348966c75afb1de4dc71a9798.jpg&h=d7bbe2d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195425_7e40d6e4c1be56043a2d89f554e7699a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195425_7e40d6e4c1be56043a2d89f554e7699a.jpg&h=a3bf3504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195428_df6bffcb857dcc78bb622cb80dabe3df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195428_df6bffcb857dcc78bb622cb80dabe3df.jpg&h=c6c83966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195431_6d6535319addf94d38760631f2d7a5c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195431_6d6535319addf94d38760631f2d7a5c0.jpg&h=0d3f5540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195432_06538f7ef197b7713ba460ec9266003b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195432_06538f7ef197b7713ba460ec9266003b.jpg&h=812ac1bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">目前遊戲的事前登錄人數已突破15萬人，是故已確定遊戲推出後，全部玩家將可獲得相等於一個十連轉蛋份量的600個鑽石以及「☆5傭兵確定券」。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲核心內容是陣營配置，先在戰前佈置我方十體傭兵角色，再在戰鬥階段時接雙方角色的攻勢移動順來互相攻?。作品之內有多達300名角色，而且全都均可提升至最高階級別。<br />\n<br />\nIOS：<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1299021478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid1299021478&d=l6hWxyUZxcYB2fkPV4X2e54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=34ae3d59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1299021478</a><br />\nAN：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.neowizgames.game.browndust.srpg.global\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.neowizgames.game.browndust.srpg.global&d=l6hWxyUZxcYB2fkPV4X2e54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=36048973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.neowizgames.game.browndust.srpg.global</a><br />\nQooApp：<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/6042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F6042&d=l6hWxyUZxcYB2fkPV4X2e54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ec3373a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/6042</a></div>"},{"pid":"e1444f7b3df895942cf2873f145870c24b2379f8","tid":598383,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:39:59.000Z","msg":"玩左日棄留名<br />\n利申抽唔到想要既首抽棄"},{"pid":"cb9015a09f01ec3b23ae3a10c8092ef8d2d2efec","tid":598383,"uid":1522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>【照顧絲打/基巴區】</strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195804_42f30c25e5fef448db62d7c6c9b6762b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195804_42f30c25e5fef448db62d7c6c9b6762b.jpg&h=72244847&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195807_b0341269fd21723090a3169103438a34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195807_b0341269fd21723090a3169103438a34.jpg&h=38fd3b17&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195810_b5fab7dd8a30734ee53ea2a46db8b6be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195810_b5fab7dd8a30734ee53ea2a46db8b6be.jpg&h=26ba679f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195812_821682b225905978953e0f97e65b0ab9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195812_821682b225905978953e0f97e65b0ab9.jpg&h=88a5ccde&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195814_abf34b3c931bee1138125c896371a5d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195814_abf34b3c931bee1138125c896371a5d9.jpg&h=d46a4d33&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/123528_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F123528_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d65c72b9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">【攻略】<br />\n<br />\n日版速刷首抽方法 (遊戲內建)<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=32104&amp;snA=4&amp;tnum=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D32104%26snA%3D4%26tnum%3D3&d=l6hWxyUZxcYB2fkPV4X2e54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5c228410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=32104&amp;snA=4&amp;tnum=3</a><br />\n右上角設定<br />\nPLUG下方那排日文 點下去<br />\n打上Reset 就重來了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【日本評價網】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wiki.denfaminicogamer.jp/browndust/%E3%83%AA%E3%82%BB%E3%83%9E%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%82%AD%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0?comment=3#comment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.denfaminicogamer.jp%2Fbrowndust%2F%25E3%2583%25AA%25E3%2582%25BB%25E3%2583%259E%25E3%2583%25A9%25E3%2583%25A9%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2582%25AD%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2582%25B0%3Fcomment%3D3%23comment&d=l6hWxyUZxcYB2fkPV4X2e54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f3125a88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.denfaminicogamer.jp/browndust/%E3%83%AA%E3%82%BB%E3%83%9E%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%82%AD%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0?comment=3#comment</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【大陸仔評價】</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://img.ngacn.cc/attachments/mon_201803/07/bwQ5-8dk6ZiT1kShs-ob.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fimg.ngacn.cc%2Fattachments%2Fmon_201803%2F07%2FbwQ5-8dk6ZiT1kShs-ob.jpg&h=a8fde95d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://c.kekeke.cc/t/FmVevFK97u.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fc.kekeke.cc%2Ft%2FFmVevFK97u.jpeg&h=7c7dc4c0&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">【韓服圖鑑】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mega.nz/#!ZBAUWIKY!XxV3tpkf_YXJ10VkklJbGCDQOws4rhJi10APPqHmer8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmega.nz%2F%23%21ZBAUWIKY%21XxV3tpkf_YXJ10VkklJbGCDQOws4rhJi10APPqHmer8&d=l6hWxyUZxcYB2fkPV4X2e54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=71fb79d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mega.nz/#!ZBAUWIKY!XxV3tpkf_YXJ10VkklJbGCDQOws4rhJi10APPqHmer8</a></div>"},{"pid":"9f6e7daf19900a31fa43ad2e8689af825c63dc5f","tid":598383,"uid":1522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:43:01.000Z","msg":"Q&amp;A:<br />\n<br />\nQ:隻驚洗唔洗刷首抽<br />\nA:最好就刷 因為抽五星機率只係1% 十次十連都唔中係經常既事<br />\n<br />\nQ:刷到歌基+是但一隻開唔開波好<br />\nA:開 再問就ban<br />\n<br />\nQ:課咩野包係最抵屌<br />\nA:新手500%<br />\n<br />\nQ:隻驚好似好複雜 唔知點樣玩<br />\nA:呢隻驚好似捉棋咁 放錯人錯順序都會影響哂成場結果 自己慢慢摸索啦<br />\n<br />\nQ:好多體力唔知點洗好<br />\nA:新手一開始就衝主線 唔夠打就刷符紋/肥料升主力<br />\n<br />\nQ:無錢又無肥 幾時先有得刷肥關<br />\nA:星期五至日或日本假期特定時間 <br />\n<br />\nQ:抽咩pool好<br />\nA:2222222<br />\n<br />\nQ:抽到好多三星做唔做升星肥好<br />\nA:唔做 好多三星都有用 廢既就將佢+9 兩隻+9合一隻原四<br />\n<br />\nQ:抽到重覆五星食唔食好<br />\nA:隻野勁就食 廢就做升星肥<br />\n<br />\nQ:sup狀態會放邊 唔識用<br />\nA:下一個順序<br />\n<br />\nQ:隻驚肝唔肝<br />\nA:唔肝、因為可以掛機打素材，但係唔會失樂趣 因為掛機成日會唔夠打 而且pvp 公會戰 地下城 搶礦 打符文高層 全部都係要用腦去諗同試 <br />\n<br />\nQ:無課玩唔玩到<br />\nA:玩到 育成Game課左只會資源黎得較快 <br />\n<br />\nQ:六魔星點有<br />\nA:無得首抽 用魔幣換<br />\n<br />\nQ:點樣買體係最抵<br />\nA:神秘島係有粉既情況 係交易所用石刷商店買體 抵過直接用石買<br />\n<br />\nQ:敏捷有咩用<br />\nA:被攻擊時有機率觸發減35%傷 debuff持續時間減半<br />\n<br />\nQ:可唔可以一次過升星 逐隻逐隻禁好煩<br />\nA:可以 去升星畫面左下個傭兵選擇 <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/124319_df4328360824ac5145095d454cd2a143.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F124319_df4328360824ac5145095d454cd2a143.png&h=f2053715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">提防假連登公會 3會同5會唔係連登仔開</span></span>"},{"pid":"77e47771b32ef01d90ca6c12b8976d7412257370","tid":598383,"uid":1522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:55:21.000Z","msg":"黎緊有九尾？"},{"pid":"4fccdf9142d834eadb0a79d3c4d830f7e7d44616","tid":598383,"uid":13275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:56:25.000Z","msg":"仆你個街咁快又出9尾要課金了"},{"pid":"751ac002ded0d1fe0e6c4d9ee160814692197b2c","tid":598383,"uid":1522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:56:52.000Z","msg":"做乜又開多一個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91152f53bdeb67467e8f5cfb912521c34c88ad8","tid":598383,"uid":48109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:56:56.000Z","msg":"唔係1001開POST咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}